snippet.title: Amber Interviews Vivek Chibber on "The ABC's of Capitalism" | Chapo Trap House | Bonus Episode FULL
snippet.description:
buy our book: http://www.chapotraphouse.com/book 
http://www.soundcloud.com/chapo-trap-house 
http://patreon.com/chapotraphouse 



Amber talks to writer and professor of sociology Vivek Chibber about "The ABC's of Capitalism," his new series of pamphlets for Jacobin.

Vivek Chibber is the editor of Catalyst: A Journal of Theory and Strategy, which is published by Jacobin, along with The ABCs of Capitalism. You can pick up a copy of the ABC's of Capitalism here: https://www.jacobinmag.com/store/product/56


 #chapotraphouse #chapo
